name: semantic-ui-react-with-redux-forms
description:
Example showing how to integrate Semantic UI React with Redux Forms. This ain't your run of the mill normal input fields. I tried building some intricate input fields that we might need in the real world!

Form Input integration examples:
- Basic Input Field
- Searchable Dropdown Field
- Google Maps Field
- [Incomplete] Checkbox Field that only appears when user answers the yes/no first
